Happy Saturdayyy✨ Let’s do a quick recap of our @mnryouth YWE Bible Study link up!  It was a whole vibee! Young women that love God came together and studied about God’s Grace! We laughed, prayed, applied the word to our personal lives, created friendships, and left better! 
For the person that thinks you have to be alone to walk with God, think again! You don’t have to be isolated to be consecrated. There’s other young people out there that have the same desire and love for Jesus, just like you! Part of my calling is to cultivate environments for young Christian women to find Jesus and find our community. 🤍  It’s necessary for spiritual growth. YWE is that community.
We gotta do it again soon!👀 
#Sisterhood #christianwomencommunity #YWE

PASSION 2024 was life changing. 
Our generation isn’t lost, there is a body of unashamed young believers that have a pure heart for Jesus. A generation committed to keeping His name famous. 60,000 18-25 year olds filled the Mercedes Benz stadium to worship and grow deeper in our faith!  Such a beautiful experience🥹
I left passion with my passion reignited! There’s a great work to do in the kingdom and my YES has been renewed! 
Thank you @passion268 🙌🏽
